{"tid":2408301,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]加泰隆尼亞議會選舉結果直播","createTime":"2021-02-14T20:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T00:59:55.000Z","uid":104122,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fbeb69210b50d984d4d7add54e8dc7c854eb2136","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:15:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ara.cat/politica/resultats-eleccions-parlament-catalunya-14-febrer-14-f-2021-erc-psc-jxcat-pdcat-cup-comuns-pp-ciutadans-vox_1_3872759.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ara.cat%2Fpolitica%2Fresultats-eleccions-parlament-catalunya-14-febrer-14-f-2021-erc-psc-jxcat-pdcat-cup-comuns-pp-ciutadans-vox_1_3872759.html&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1ee51277\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ara.cat/politica/resultats-eleccions-parlament-catalunya-14-febrer-14-f-2021-erc-psc-jxcat-pdcat-cup-comuns-pp-ciutadans-vox_1_3872759.html</a>"},{"pid":"f5707a8e03399041e9f7dae165ae753f349d9a6b","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:21:49.000Z","msg":"政黨簡介：<br />\n<br />\nPSC - Partit dels Socialistes de Catalunya<br />\n現任西班牙執政黨<br />\n中間派不主張獨立<br />\n<br />\nJxCAT - Junts per Catalunya<br />\nPuigdemont 個黨<br />\n2017 declare咗獨立而主席流亡比利時<br />\n主張獨立<br />\n<br />\nERC - Esquerra Republicana de Catalunya<br />\n上屆Quim Torre個黨<br />\n上年啱啱俾西班牙政府revoke咗個位<br />\n主張republic of Spain，移除西班牙國王<br />\n<br />\n依加主要係依三個大黨打緊<br />\n暫時三分天下"},{"pid":"8f36657061298d58cd3a044a52853553af57c24c","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:29:07.000Z","msg":"細黨派：<br />\n<br />\nPP - Partit Popular<br />\n曾經掌權十幾年嘅右派最大政黨<br />\n大概同依加民建聯差唔多<br />\n但因貪污依加右派大多唔投佢，轉投其他右派<br />\n<br />\nCds - Ciutadans<br />\n中間偏右<br />\n<br />\nVox <br />\n新興極右派<br />\n主張恢復死刑、停止接收難民、抵制任何加泰主義<br />\n<br />\nPDeCAT - Partit Dem&ograve;crata de Catalunya<br />\n主獨右派<br />\n唔同意一般左派嘅前衛政策<br />\n主張加泰獨立後成為西歐其中一個經濟大體系"},{"pid":"661eecc85b277f55f3136d5855fa0d9f4df930d3","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"暫時獨立左派 - 留西左派 - 右派三分天下"},{"pid":"ef4ec35e8cb2defcff25daa7271c9a8ad16bbd38","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:33:09.000Z","msg":"但因為依個二月十四號嘅選舉係疫情期間<br />\nPresident Pedro Sanchez唔想主獨黨嘅Pere Aragon&egrave;s 繼續執政先格硬執行<br />\n好多左派因為唔想疫情繼續發生都冇去投票"},{"pid":"4012da5d452558546239f4931787ab2f1bfc670a","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:35:13.000Z","msg":"依個選舉係因為西班牙政府先前強制加泰主席換人<br />\n詳見：<br />\n馬德里最高法院一致通過罷免加泰隆尼亞主席Quim Torra<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2221967\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2221967</a>"},{"pid":"166275860900d158a14bf4fcb2965f461f4a197c","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjNnHtr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjNnHtr.png&h=d59e8c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時左 - 右 = 66% - 33%<br />\n(PSC中間偏右 ERC、JUNTS左)<br />\n左派有兩大黨、右派得一大<br />\n如果左派傾唔掂數而右派可以組到coalition<br />\n可能今屆加泰議會會由右派執政"},{"pid":"3d53d95f6a2d9f61283af31479ffdf69c62fad00","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae65fbf89e7f0588110d00573edfda27fc20999","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiqAh3g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiqAh3g.png&h=c52bc231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以首都巴塞為中心嘅選區大多投偏右嘅留西派<br />\n舐西 = 發大財<br />\n<br />\nTarragona 主要投ERC<br />\n因為佢哋都唔係太想獨立<br />\n但想有個公平嘅representation of catalans<br />\n<br />\nRural areas 全部獨派咁濟"},{"pid":"2280d3178ce4c601ddfaf2c6fc34a916a33ce5bd","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07556ed5ae46babe723d04c6bb4a1892a2986dbc","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ccma.cat/tv3/directe/tv3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccma.cat%2Ftv3%2Fdirecte%2Ftv3%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=6ea0aa67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ccma.cat/tv3/directe/tv3/</a>"},{"pid":"c4cb6e27b94b2c7e84f5d9816dc4353ef6282e9f","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bd2b8f49f82d0195d319b0cb205fe0b1b53eee","tid":2408301,"uid":104122,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T20:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7LsTDZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7LsTDZ.png&h=2b511482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驗咗差唔多一半票<br />\n極右VOX 有11席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明佢嘅政治目標係大西班牙主義反加泰<br />\n廢老藍絲真多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b322bf8a04de1a97325abd65269427e56bddaad0","ti